A VIDEO of a Mr Price store being robbed has being shared on social media. According to Yusuf Abramjee who posted the video, the robbery took place at Mr Price, Joburg CBD near the MTN Taxi Rank. In the video, a man armed with a firearm is seen walking in while tellers are assisting customers. He then instructs them to open tills and orders customers to lie down. His accomplices empty the tills while he takes phones from the customers.   